Package com.arjuna.mw.wscf.model.as.coordinator.twophase.messages

Class Summary
AfterCompletion A Synchronization participant is informed that the coordinator it is registered with has completed the two-phase protocol and in what state it finished, i.e., confirmed or cancelled.
BeforeCompletion A Synchronization participant is informed that the coordinator it is registered with is about to complete the two-phase protocol and in what state it finishing, i.e., confirmed or cancelled.
ForgetHeuristic The participant made a post-prepare choice that was contrary to that which the coordinator told it to do.
NestedCancel The coordinator is nested and is cancelling.
NestedConfirm The coordinator is nested and is confirming.
NestedOnePhaseCommit If only a single participant is registered with a two-phase coordinator then it is possible for the coordinator to optimise the commit stage and not have to execute two phases: the outcome of the coordination is ultimately in the hands of the participant and not the coordinator.
NestedPrepare The coordinator is nested and is preparing.
TopLevelCancel The coordinator is top-level and is cancelling.
TopLevelConfirm The coordinator is top-level and is confirming.
TopLevelOnePhaseCommit If only a single participant is registered with a two-phase coordinator then it is possible for the coordinator to optimise the commit stage and not have to execute two phases: the outcome of the coordination is ultimately in the hands of the participant and not the coordinator.
TopLevelPrepare The coordinator is top-level and is preparing.
